'''AGASUMO'''

Intara ya [[IProvense ya Mwaro|Mwaro]] izwi cane cane kubera aho bita '''Agasumo''' "falls" '''ka Mwaro''', ahantu  hari haragenewe ibanga ryo [[Kubandwa]]. Imbere y’uko Abapatiri baza mu [[Uburundi|Burundi]], Abarundi bose bemera [[Imana]] (one God) hanyuma bagasenga [[Kiranga]], ariwe yari icabona c’Imana. Kiranga bamusenga babicishije mu Kubandwa.

